abstract: STAMFORD, Conn., June 15 -- The 11th annual Debutante Ball of the Junior League of Stamford-Norwalk was held tonight at the Stamford Yacht Club. Mrs. Rudolph Eberstadt Jr. and Mrs. Alan H. Bede were co-chairmen for the event, which benefited the league's Community Trust Fund.
